reviewText: I would characterize this is a "self learning" course where the instructor points the way, but the student has to fill in all the blanks.  I would suggest that prospective students have a good introductory econometrics text on hand for reference to fill in the missing details.
It was a good review.  It would be useful to have some tutorials for some the R lab problems.   Providing copies of the slides and a suggested textbook would be useful.
